overview.en: SAFE network focuses on privacy protection, strengthens secure payment, optimizes asset privacy, imports cross chain assets and stable currency, creates SAFESwap trading field, expands more commercial applications, and aims to build a global privacy protection ecosystem. Token SAFE accross-chain into ETH network, start a new DEFI trip
overview.zh: 安网（SAFE）专注于大规模安全支付，优化资产隐私，引入跨链资产和稳定币，打造safeswap交易场，拓展更多商业化应用，旨在构建一个全球范围的隐私保护生态圈。SAFE跨链至ETH，开启DEFI新征程。
